  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 Orthopedic — Tibial Tray Contact Stress Credibility Assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite-element prediction of tibial tray contact stress in a total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant under physiological loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict peak contact stress and stress distribution at the tibial tray–bone interface at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed. Achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for all factors. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on material property inputs is performed. Decision: Accepted.",
