      "rationale": "Abaqus 2022 is a commercially validated FE solver with documented V&V history. The simulation workflow is version-controlled in Git; input decks, mesh files, and post-processing scripts are archived in a controlled repository with access logs. An independent analyst reproduced all three loading-scenario results from archived inputs, confirming reproducibility. SQA documentation meets MRL 3 requirements; achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
